				spab
a quick tool to replace space intendation for tabs in your source or text files

*********************************************************************************

usage: ./spab [input file] [output file] [number of spaces (must be >= 4)]

BUG: if you pass the same file name to input file and output file expecting the 
original file will be rewritten, no. it deletes everything in the file. so if
you're gonna use this set the input and output files to different stuff, for example:

			./spab file.c file_tabbed.c 4
